<plot>Sophie died in a car crash, she was 28 years old. Her close friends in grief reunite. The film portrays three stages of their grief. From the silent contemplation of their loss to the need to escape by celebrating life that finally leads to the acknowledgment of the death and their own solitude.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?605827</url></doc>
